text: aur jabaki unamen se ek giroh ne kaha, "ai yasaribavaalo, tumhaare lie thaharane ka koee mauqa nahin. atah laut chalo." aur unaka ek giroh nabee se yah kahakar (vaapas jaane kee) anumati chaah raha tha ki "hamaare ghar asurakshit hai." yadyapi ve asurakshit na the. ve to bas bhaagana chaahate the
